timeline.message:
Parquet: Handle nested column schema changes when subfield pruning is enabled

After schema is changed (new field at depth > 1) and when trying to read files with old schema
we end up with a situation where the type of the newly added field type is derived incorrectly.
When this new field type is merged with type of other subfields within the same column, we get
the following error/.

